org.alienideology.jcord.handle.managers

Class IWebhookManager.WebhookMessageBuilder

  • java.lang.Object
    • org.alienideology.jcord.handle.managers.IWebhookManager.WebhookMessageBuilder
  • Enclosing interface:
    IWebhookManager

    public static class IWebhookManager.WebhookMessageBuilder
extends java.lang.Object
    A simple message builder for webhooks. Main difference to the MessageBuilder is that webhooks' messages may have temporary overridden names and avatars.
